    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Aliens Group Consulting Pvt Ltd in Amritsar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Aliens Group Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nAliens Group Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aliens Group Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
